  "id": "MTt789wo",
  "slug": "cit-enchanted-books-hotfix",
  "title": "CIT: Hotfix for Enchanted Books",
  "description": "Making Resource Packs With CITs for Enchanted Books Work on Newer Versions",
  "body": "<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CIPYHp0.png\" alt=\"Title\" /></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint.svg?url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%3Fusername%3DMarsThePlanet%26type%3Dpatrons&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cit-enchanted-books-hotfix\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1086209?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cit-enchanted-books-hotfix\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/cit-enchanted-books-hotfix?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a> </strong></h5></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This mod fixes texture packs with CITs for enchanted books on versions 1.20.5 to 1.21.3. It is meant as a temporary fix until this functionality comes back to mods such as CIT Resewn or Optifine. The showcase below is using my texture pack <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/different-textures-for-enchanted-books\">Enchanted Books from Mars</a>. But this mod is compatible with almost all other texture packs adding more enchanted book textures.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0Muod80.png\" width=\"484\"/></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p></center>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Configuration</strong></summary>\n<p>You can configure this mod directly in-game or edit the JSON file <code>config/cithotfix.json</code> in your profile folder. If you're using Fabric and want to adjust the config values in-game, you'll need to install <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/modmenu\">Mod Menu</a>.</p>\n<center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>possible_roots</b> - Sets which resource pack paths should be checked by this mod for CITs of enchanted books</p>\n</center>\n</details>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JNZ2GMV.png\"/>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/deimos-fabric-forge-neoforge\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/83sD0W8.png\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deimos\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j2GIPnt.png\"/></a>\n</p></center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/marstheplanet\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rJIRiP5.png\" /></a></p>",
